productName: Nike Women's Phoenix Waffle White/Green/Grey Sneaker
description: All-day comfort meets all-day style. Taking cues from original Blue Ribbon Sports designs and incorporating the technological advances of today, the Phoenix Waffle rises from the ashes. A redesigned Waffle tread lightens the shoe, while the increased midsole height creates an even softer ride. Check the vintage Swoosh logo and archive-inspired tongue for a modern take on classic BRS looks.(Supplier Style:FD2196-103/1)
